# toDoList environment variables
#
# Copy this file to `.env` (same directory) and fill in the real values.
# `.env` is gitignored — your actual credentials never get committed.
#
# All values are read at build time by Webpack's DefinePlugin (via dotenv)
# and substituted into `process.env.*` references in the source. They are
# baked into the bundled JS, so any value here must be safe to expose to
# the browser.

# Supabase — for the backend (database, auth, realtime).
# Get from your Supabase dashboard → Settings → API.
# The anon key is meant to be public; RLS policies enforce security.
